sanam teri kasam ( hindi : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; , urdu : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1982 indian hindi romantic drama film directed by om prakash and produced by &lt;unk&gt; khan . the film features music composed by rahul dev burman . the film was later remade in hindi as sanam teri kasam .